Extremely unsafe and disappointing experience. Driver misconduct, wrongful charges, and being stranded mid-ride ‚Äî this is what I faced. Instead of help, I was met with silence and a robotic app that offers no way to reach a real human in emergencies. Ola promised action and a refund, but nothing has been resolved. Safety and trust should never be compromised, yet both were completely ignored here. Until Ola fixes its broken support system and ensures accountability, passengers remain at risk.

Update your app and customer service, Ola Foods! Strongly recommend a customer helpline service!
